| Column | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | uuid PK | |
| `platform_id` | text unique | e.g. `mq-9b-skyguardian` |
| `name` | text | Display name |
| `country_of_origin` | text | ISO country name |
| `manufacturer` | text | |
| `dod_group` | text | Group 1–5 or NATO class |
| `role` | text[] | ISR, Strike, EW, Decoy, Relay, Swarm |
| `max_altitude_ft` | integer | |
| `max_range_km` | integer | |
| `max_endurance_hrs` | numeric | |
| `max_speed_kts` | integer | |
| `payload_kg` | numeric | |
| `combat_proven` | boolean | |
| `combat_theatres` | text[] | Ukraine, Syria, Libya, etc. |
| `status` | text | Operational / Development / Retired |
| `description` | text | |
| `specs` | jsonb | Additional KPIs |
| `created_at` | timestamptz | |

